PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781873291
OL,3,CHow a grieving mother is helping
OL,4,Cothers 'just talk'
OL,6,FJay was a musician and poet who
OL,7,Fdespite living with his own
OL,8,Fchallenges, was a much loved son and
OL,9,Ffather. Gillian smiles as she recounts
OL,10,Fhim and recalls that despite
OL,11,Feverything, they never fell out. She
OL,12,Fstarted posting his songs and
OL,13,Fcompositions online to showcase his
OL,14,Ftalent and musical legacy and then
OL,15,Fbegan to post herself about what she
OL,16,Fwas going through, her sense of loss
OL,17,Fand grief.
OL,19,FGillian admits she's a talker and says
OL,20,Fgrief is something which can be
OL,21,Finfluenced by your personality type.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
