PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1781873291
OL,3,CHow a grieving mother is helping
OL,4,Cothers 'just talk'
OL,6,FEven within her own family, Gillian
OL,7,Fsays grief has hit in different ways.
OL,8,FBut she feels for women, for mothers,
OL,9,Fthe loss is felt differently, no more
OL,10,Fthan others but different.
OL,12,FIt's in this safe space with these
OL,13,Fother women that she finds temporary
OL,14,Fsolace. Her husband asks if she ever
OL,15,Ftalks to anyone who hasn't lost a
OL,16,Fchild but Gillian says for where she
OL,17,Fis now, small talk isn't an option.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
